The initial interaction with Persephone is strange to me You get the mission to talk to her after clearing the Three Sisters which is a direct attack on her power She says she knows everything in Elysium so she should know you are working directly against her Yet she doesnt seem to care one way or the other

Even then the best route takes you through two territories to get to Asphodel I suppose there is a way to go straight there but not only is it easier but it seems to be designed for you to go south then sweep to the east through two territories on the way to Asphodel I cleared both of those before I entered Asphodel

Once you get there there are soldiers that dont attack and you can go straight to her palace She is quite cordial apologizing for attacking you when you first entered the realm and then she asks you to retrieve a horse so it can be returned to Hades Nothing really changes after you do that you get a skin for Phobos and a quest to talk to Hermes The guards are just as hostile as before in their strongholds I even took out several marble maidens stole supplies and eliminated torches of Hypnos in Asphodel

I tried reading into it it doesnt really matter what you do with the horse either I decided I want Persephone on my side so I gave it to the stable boy It sounds like you can give it to the rebels and threaten the stable boy and get the same outcome Either way you get the skin for Phobos

Im just hoping I didnt break any quests along the way I am carrying multiple quest items right now I did skip one cave that has a related quest I entered it from the wrong direction and found my way blocked I later found the other entrance but didnt go in Persephone

Please discuss anything relating to FedEx GLS or ParcelForce here Anything from your experience positive or negative questions regarding delivery wait times or delivery issues and delivery damage images all belong in this megathread

xB

 Frequently Asked Questions

xB

Who will ship my Steam Deck

xB

In North America USCA this will be FedEx RMAs are also processed by FedEx

xB

In Europe this will be GLS In the UK this will be ParcelForce or EVRI formerly known as Hermes usually in times of industrial action RMAs in Europe are by DHL

In Komodo regions we arent sure yet It will almost certainly be a large local courier service Regardless of who ships it you will receive a tracking number to follow your Decks progress

xB

Update for December  via Valve 

xB

Starting December st customers in Japan South Korea Hong Kong and  Taiwan who have already reserved their Steam Deck will receive email  confirmations to finalize their orders These orders will start shipping  on December th

xB

Were happy to announce that Steam Decks will start shipping in Japan  South Korea Hong Kong and Taiwan on December th via Komodo our  official Steam Deck distributor in these regions  Customers in these regions can reserve the Steam Deck here steamdeckkomodojp

xB

Source 

xB

Im stuck on Shipping Soon help

xB

Its normal for your order to stay on Shipping Soon for several days We usually see Steam Decks delivered within  working days after placing the order A business day is considered MonFri

xB

If it has been longer than  working days and its still on Shipping Soon you should contact Steam Support for assistance If you have tracking but are past  working days you should await your Steam Deck for longer unless it has been  working days since your last tracking update in which case you should contact Steam Support

xB

My tracking says preadvice  awaiting parcel help

xB

This is a normal step in the process this means your parcel is somewhere between Valves warehouse and your delivery providers first sorting hub Parcels are not scanned until they reach this hub and therefore it can show as preadvice  awaiting parcel even if they do currently have the parcel

xB

This usually changes within  working day though dont be alarmed as it can take up to  working days working days MonFri If its been longer than that you should contact Steam Support

xB

Do FedExGLSParcelForce deliver on Sundays

xB

FedEx delivers to  of the US population on a SundaySundaySunday

xB

In Europe as with most delivery companies GLS  ParcelForce does not typically deliver on a Sunday They may do so in times of peak demand around Christmas but outside of this its unlikely

xB

Both FedEx and GLS do deliver on Saturdays though

xB

UK My parcel is stuck in customs what do I do

xB

This can happen in both the RMA and delivery process but this will usually be sorted and cleared through customs after a short delay In uncommon cases it may take longer on a scale of working days but will still clear

xB

However if at any point the tracking says that additional information is required please contact Steam Support

xB

UK My parcel hasnt updated from the Netherlands in several days should I be concerned

xB

No you should not be concerned This is because there is no tracking update between it leaving the Netherlands Hub and it arriving in the UK for customs checks Depending on several events outside of the control of GLSParcelForce there are many different reasons why this could take a long period of time

xB

My Steam Deck is delayed Im annoyed

xB

Sorry to hear that your Steam Deck has been delayed Unfortunately as with any delivery service its possible for issues and delays to occur during the delivery process

xB

So long as your shipping provider is giving you frequent updates and has not elapsed more than  working days without an update hang tight

xB

If you havent received an update in over  working days MonFri please contact Steam Support

xB

My Steam Deck is brokenstolenlost from delivery help

xB

You should contact Steam Support as soon as possible so that a replacement can be arranged

xB

One of the most certain narratives is the AI token and Decrypt provides a solid primer in what they are Another such narrative involves ProofofStake and Staking to which The Defiant has published their State of Proof of Stake report to supplant Brian Armstrong however notes that the SEC may be intent on banning retail staking More to come on this magmahot topic

In the legal realm Craig Faketoshi Wright loses his day in court as the judges deem that the Bitcoin file format cant be copyrighted Hermes wins its case over an artist in a landmark NFT trial Judge denies a motion allowing SBF to use messaging apps  as he has been known to attempt to contact and influence witnesses and key persons isnt that a crime in itself And speaking of crime  South Korean authorities fly to Serbia in pursuit of Do Kwon concurrently the nation is developing a cryptocurrency tracking system due for this year An MP from St Maarten launches a bid to adopt Tron as legal tender and Bice successfully launches a prepaid crypto card with Mastercard in Brazil

Harry and his  year old wife are sat in their cramped home She decries the neighbours have  bathrooms and we have only  Its so rough waking up in a subtropical climate in the worlds sixth most affluent neighborhood and still not being able to have what other couples have  bathrooms   


Harry adds All we ever wanted was to live a normal life just like everyone else But Im really worried for my childrens future The  million pound inheritance we had when we fled the UK is all we had when we arrived here All we wanted was to give our children a normal life Instead we have to explain to them why little McKaylah and little Jamison from across the street do have a yacht when we are forced to spend our holidays in the Bahamas   


Megan softly weeps and dries her tears on an Hermes blanket  I just cant believe it has come to this We had so many dreams for our children and now  she gestures across the cramped  square meter living room We managed to get a few odd jobs since arriving and have managed to scrimp together  million dollars but how is one supposed to live off of that for any length of time with inflation numbers like this Harry put an arm over her shoulder and whispers sweetly My love Dont fret think about the palm trees of providence  


Megan adds If I wouldve been a  white I surely wouldnt have had to put up with this nonsense Harrys face tenses Its all just so unfair he says When my brother dated my now sister in law they were given none of the special treatment Megan has been given Megan was given  staff a fulltime security detail an invite to Sandringham before we were engaged offered to accompany the Queen Square that with Kate who was chased by paparazzi whilst only a fresh grad without any support no special invitations or even security Why hasnt Megan gotten the same treatment the rest of the family has gotten   


Megan composes herself and says I just know other people dont have to suffer like this Why were we dealt this hand in life Having been born into a family where theres generational trauma and favoritism uncles make bad jokes and family members sometimes even die Who else has to deal with any of that   


When we first started dating we were treated like rockstars Especially when I mentioned I was mixed race   she leans in  You know they celebrated in the streets of South Africa just like they did when Mandela was freed Harry smiles We were send on a semi royal tour of the country the plebs paid for our weddings Daddy bought us a cottage and everyone was cheering us on for being a fresh wind and the type of modern couple the family needed Megan And then  She snaps her fingers  stories began to leak about how I mistreated staff Harry And how I threw a tantrum over a tiara that wasnt mine then shit really hit the fan when we belittled and insulted the British press every single time for sticking to the agreements we had made with them

Heres the full report and the main infographic for mobile users

Methodology

 Methodology drafting Industry research and expert interviews inform the Index targets and metrics selected to measure progress The first draft of the methodology is devised
 Sustainability Council consultations Our Sustainability Council reviews the methodology in full and partakes in consultations to refine the targets and metrics These are finalised and shared with the Council
 Companies sent questionnaires Companies are notified of their inclusion in the project and are invited to complete a questionnaire of the metrics with publicly available evidence This is optional and not all companies participated
 Research companies BoF researchers review each company and populate the questionnaire with evidence of relevant public disclosures to award preliminary points crosschecking and verifying evidence in responses submitted by the companies
 Companies receive preliminary results and fact checks BoF researchers conduct quality assurance checks to ensure companies have been scored consistently and fairly against the metrics before sharing preliminary results with the companies along with any fact checks
 Responses are reviewed Fact check responses and additional comments from the companies are reviewed and individual consultations with Council members over specific metrics take place
 Data is compiled and finalised If a company provided additional information or disputed a finding this was reviewed and then either adjusted or not as considered appropriate
 Final analysis and report prepared Data from each company is compiled into one complete dataset which is used to determine final scores and points of analysis BUSINESS OF FASHIONS SUSTAINABILITY INDEX AKA HOW SUSTAINABLE ARE LUXURY BRANDS REALLY

Hello everyone 

Today we will be discussing the controversy surrounding the most recent Toy Stories Campaign 

If you are unaware Balenciaga was accused of sexualising children and childrens toys due to a recent campaign photoshoot release Well be going over the facts The rumours And the response This will be the only thread in which to discuss this manner because over time posts which already stand will be brigaded and descend into chaos 

The facts A few days ago Balenciaga began running advertisements on their website as part of their SpringSummer  campaign One portion of which is the Toy Stories The photoshoot featured children some of which were holding stuffed bears which were adorned in what appeared to be BDSMBondage gear Also within these photographs appeared to be a Supreme Court document outlining the decision of a  case United States v Williams which upheld the PROTECT Act set by the federal government in the case of something we cannot describe on Reddit 

The rumours Many many rumours have been flying around stating that Balenciaga and its parent company Kering are attempting to promote these products for children Or intentionally attempting to make the content of which normal for children As stated by Balenciaga in their official response to this controversy this was not their intention And the children should never have been exposed to such products

Some allege that Gabriele Galimberti was the mastermind behind these sets This is UNTRUE Gabriele Galimberti was simply the photographer who has no say in the set pieces or what they may or may not contain What is also untrue is that the image containing the Supreme Court document was also an image taken by him We cannot stress enough that you should never ever send hate messages or death threats to anyone for any reason whatsoever

The response Balenciaga has removed the campaign from their website along with all social media platforms Balenciaga has stated they are pursuing legal action against those who designed this photoshoot and the inclusion of such documents in the photoshoot Balenciaga Campaign Controversy

This post is Part One in a series intended to warn all unsuspecting Text RPGers who may happen upon a game called Achaea Dreams of Divine Lands before they make the grand mistake I did and drop a lot of cash into a supposedly free to play game ha thinking itd be easy to catch up with longer term players and open the door to limitless RP and combat potential

My plan is to cover topics like Why Retirement is a Scam The Legality of Loot Boxes and The Great Microtransaction Con along with delving into some little known history of the game its administration and the coverups the admin supposedly dont want anyone to know about

At some point Id also like to address issues of gender and sexuality in Achaea as well since there seems to be a lot of information readily available on how a game open to yearolds handles such situations Harassment forced textual relations and sexual fraternization with and amid the games administration are all possible future subjects

If this interests you read on

The first and perhaps most important thing that anyone needs to know about Achaea is that a lot of what its website promises is not legit A few of the more egregious claims are as follows lets delve a little into each one

 Virtually all aspects of a city are run by playersOUR TRUTH DETECTOR found this claim to be SOMEWHAT FALSE

Achaeas cities are run by players but this claim is actually advertising the potential for any player new to the game or old to take part in such organizational leadership The reality Ive uncovered is that Achaeas cities have been run since their inception by a handful of Garden think Divine Administration behind the scenes and in the sandbox of the world loyals and whales

One only needs to look at the oldest citizens of the game and its organizational hierarchy and history published on Achaeas own site and wiki to see evidence of this Since its inception in  organization after organization sprung up in the game with founders who worked closely with game administration to create their own little space and even new classes in the game

This of course makes total sense You build outward from charismatic and knowledgeable individuals in any organization But the foothold these and other players have in the game is somewhat staggering when compared to other text RPGs and visual MMOs

Since the formation and reformation in the case of Targossas of the main principalities each city has had what looks to be a revolving door of ruling council members But after discussing the game behind the scenes with longerterm players many of these individuals are just alts alterative characters of the same players who simply have a Godgranted stranglehold on RP leadership in the game

The same can be said for its Houses Many longplaying Achaeans I met and spoke with said that the sad reality is that whenever new players move in any of these organizations outside the vision of the games producers they are summarily dispensed from their roles and blacklisted to ensure they do not move back into leadership again That really turned me off especially when I witnessed some really questionable outcastings and enemyings in the city I belonged to in game that were almost entirely motivated by what appeared to be Divine influence

This hidden micromanagement of what is advertised to be an open world full of leadership potential is  therefore in my opinion one of the Achaeas dirtiest little secrets From Divine Administration metagaming with their former incharacter friends Divine are chosen from a pool of Achaeas current playerbase and rarely forego those friendships despite supposed rules against fraternization to Producers inhabiting denizen forms to outcast and blackball players stories some published in various forms online from players and former Divine persist and tell the tale of a much more controlled state of gameplay existence

 Achaea has an elaborate system of highly fleshedout GodsOUR TRUTH DETECTOR found this claim to be SOMEWHAT FALSE

Achaeas current Pantheon has  members Aegis Aurora Babel Deucalion Gaia Lorielan Neraeos Ourania Pandora Phaestus Prospero Sartan Scarlatti Tlalaiad Twilight Valnurana and Vastar

At one time Achaea had as many as as  divine the aforementioned divine plus Aeon Aeyr Agatheis Apollyon Artemis Balmet Caspian Clementius Daedalus Eris Glacius Hermes Indrani Kastalia Keresis Khalas Lucretius Lupus Matsuhama Maya Melantha Miramar Mithraea Oneiros Pandemonium Pentharian Raclawice Sarapis SElene Tarah Thoth and Varian

Although not all these Divine were actually played by volunteers what Achaea calls the behind the scenes workers who mostly are required to work  hours a week for the opportunity to play these roles without any compensation the majority were A few were historical characters in the games lore though and some were solely eventdriven roles abandoned after happenstance ingame

Today the majority of these Divine rosters are either dead or missing Out of the  currently existing members of the games fleshed out Pantheon yes well give them that point  each God has deepdeveloped lore that is truly top notch although that all changes each time a new divine volunteer takes up one of the roles as evidenced from history ingame and on their own wiki and website only Lorielan who is rumoured to be played by the games main producer is actually awake and active at this time  and shes not been seen since June  when she wrestled a portion of a city away from another Divines unwanted control a roleplay event

Going down the list I approximate this as the current level of actual Divine activity

 Aegis left Achaea amid the COVID pandemic
 Aurora has been reincarnated multiple times and is currently inactive
 Babel has been reincarnated multiple times and is currently inactive
 Deucalion has been reincarnated multiple times and is currently inactive
 Gaia has been reincarnated multiple times and recently announced her inactivity
 Neraeos is inactive
 Ourania is inactive
 Pandora is rumoured to be inactive following her most recent ingame series of events
 Phaestus works solely behind the scenes now when hes not creating oneoff events for his ingame friends and loyals
 Prospero is inactive
 Sartan is inactive
 Scarlatti is inactive It is rumoured that a player once paid thousands of dollars to bypass all Celani divine admin training protocol and played the role into the murky mudsexed ground
 Tlalaiad is active but holds a behind the scenes role mainly
 Twilight has been reincarnated multiple times and his most recent incarnation is inactive after moving over to become the producer of Iron Realm Entertainments Aetolia
 Valnurana has been inactive before her reallife spouse Tecton left the main producers role in  to champion IREs failed Starmourn venture
 Vastar has been reincarnated multiple times and is currently inactive

Some sightings of these Gods inrealm are purportedly the result of Producers assuming their roles for eventbased sheigans leaving the serious roleplay value of their highly fleshedout Gods in question

 Smaller tighter friendlier communitiesOUR TRUTH DETECTOR found this claim to be ALMOST ENTIRELY FALSE

Achaea is mainly comprised of cliques of people Although these are definitely smaller and tighter communities than found in many RPG and MMO games they are not necessarily friendlier despite the advertisement to the contrary

Just like in high school these groups of players breed an atmosphere of exclusivity and toxicity Rather than the friendly highly collaborative open world of possibilities that Achaea advertises not everyone has equal input in most instances And like most cliques they are darn hard to enter and become a valued part of the group

Instead there are Mean Girls in every city and organization in the game who use players desire to fit in and belong to their advantage There are typically  domit persons in every organization who are spreading gossip based on their personal past with others even to the point of outing players who have retired Achaeas system of starting over on a new anonymous character Discord plays a big role in this

Anyone who has ever served as a manager knows that good directors or game producers in this game do not tolerate cliques and instead foster community and inclusiveness with healthy competition to help spur innovation and engagement Sadly we do not find such leaders in Achaea at present

Management openly sanctions fraternization allowing divine to befriend and communicate with players on their official discord Ive been invited and participated in a conversation with a Divine myself there already work ingame to endorse one group of people or individual players over others and perpetuate an illusion of a safe roleplay environment while subtly and sometimes quite openly criticizing certain players in various venues particularly Discord who dont get on board with their intended gameplay

 The Nexus Client  the best way to play AchaeaOUR TRUTH DETECTOR found this claim to be SOMEWHAT FALSE

After starting out on a few newbie characters it quickly became apparent that the top combatants in the game do not utilize Achaeas Nexus Client Most in my experience utilize Mudlet and a package created by one of Achaeas own players that is known as AK affliction tracking

I liked Nexus as a newbie myself but I did find it jarring in the respect that this is a text game and the main draw of Nexus is its visual components There is just a real disconnection here for me

Although I cannot go into real depth about this particular claim a poll of a random  players throughout the months of September through November found that  were using a client other than Nexus There has to be a reason for this and I would love to hear your opinions on it and incorporate them into a future post in this series

 The freedom of choice and possibilities in the game are endlessOUR TRUTH DETECTOR found this claim to be SOMEWHAT FALSE

Players are largely boxed in by their choices in Achaea Choose a class that is factional and youre locked into a particular city Divine followers face a similar hazard Make a wrong move and forget about it You lose all your friends your family may disown you and youll likely be mischaracterized to the hilt to justify the harsh repercussions

The possibilities of what can be are largely overshadowed by three things

 Longterm players who will quote game lore and supposed canon at you and tell you that youre wrong and cannot possibly RP things
 Cliques of players who control the various organizations and castigate anyone who steps outside the boundaries of the roleplay they deem to be acceptable
 Divine producers who are unwilling to allow anyone to intentionally or unintentionally circumvent their intended roleplay vision for the realm

Another thing that I came across in this text RPG is the existence of a subclass of player who are basically blacklisted from joining any organization At first I thought this to be a small group of RPGers who had simply done some things so nefarious that they were cast out from the communitys inner circles yet were not bad enough to be shrubbed Achaeas version of a ban however upon inspection it seems that personal bias against individual players is what is really at work which is just sad because most of these individuals have invested thousands of reallife dollars in their characters



To sum things up never in my  years of playing RPGs and MMOs have I run across a more closed and limited gaming world than Achaea Thats just my opinion though and I would love to hear yours as well as ideas for new topics in this series of posts Ill be trying to release at least one a week starting in the new year Acheaa Dream of Divine Scams  Part I

Na Nekster platformi je mogoče zaenkrat investirati samo v faktoring Na hitro faktoring je odkup terjatev Podjetje izda račun in le ta ponavadi v BB poslu ni plačan takoj ampak z zamikom Ampak podjetje pa rabi denar da lahko posluje Zato proda terjatev in dobi denar danes Več o faktoringu si lahko preberete tukaj

So my current year old daily worn Common Projects Achilles are starting to look like a pair of Golden Goose and need replacing so I figured Id test the market to see if they were still the king of minimal leather sneakers I went out and got my hands on  leather sneakers across the price spectrum to figure out the best overall shoe and the best value for money Well talk about the fit the leather the build quality and more of each of these before making a final verdict Hopefully you guys enjoy this one just as much as the Joggers  TShirt Hoodies and Polo ones I did a while back

Regarding the these are frugal comments that always come

  I look at my purchases through a cost per wear lens The fact that Ive worn these  times a week for nearly five years and they still have some life in them make these the cheaper per wear by a long shot than all the cheaper options Ive tried and tossed out less than a year later Its an added bonus that they look much nicer throughout the way I didnt include things like Nike or Adidas as I wanted shoes that would compete directly with Common Projects and would last as long as they did 

For reference Im typically a  in most shoes and a  on the European scale

 Video

 All the info you need is on this post but if you want to see more details and view them on feet and side by side heres a  minute video going in depth 
 None of that of that in your face type stuff but some quality content that takes a minute to produce The joggers polo and tshirts ones are also in the library somewhere so feel free to check those out
 Link

xB

 Thursday Boots 

Well start with our cheapest and work our way up These are called the Premier Low from Thursday Boots They cost  and were ordered in a size  in the coffee color way The color did differ slightly from the images online to the pair I received Its a tad lighter than expected and barely has that dark brown to light brown gradient that I really liked when I saw them on their website

 Leather
    The leather on these felt the softest compared to the rest of the shoes featured today The outer is made of a full grain American leather and the inner is lined with a super soft sheep skin The insole is also made with vachetta which is that creamish colored natural leather you see on Louis Vuitton bags Its an added premium that I dont expect at this price point but Thursday claims it helps with shock absorption and comfort These are also the most plush out of all the shoes with a pretty thick foam between the outer and inner leathers in the tongue and the heel area 
 Sole
    The sole on these are ones that Thursday custom developed in house It features two different types of rubber a softer one on the side to help with flexibility and a stiffer one on the bottom to help with durabilityIt is board lasted which means the leather upper and the rubber sole are glued together pretty much stopping these from ever being resoled
 Styling
    Getting the technical stuff out of the way lets talk about styling and wear Theses arent my favorite looking sneakers and I think the laces have the a lot to do with that The flat laces along with the shiny eyelets make these feel like some Converse Chuck Taylors made of bougie leather The silhouette is the least minimal one here with heel sloping up heavily and the toe box being wide The break in period isnt the worst but they did squeak a good amount on the first few wears The logo stamped inside is already coming off My biggest issue is how the tongue buckles and lifts where the it meets the toe box
       Im not sure if this is because of how I have them laced or if its because thats where the tongue padding ends but it leaves a prominent crease and lifted area when these are on feet causing them to look messy
    On a side note note I found a few cases noted in prior threads where the shoes differ from pair to pair Thursday claimed this was because of different factory locations but variations this large might be a red flag for you
 Conclusion
    All that being said these are a solid pair for someone just getting into leather sneakers Although the color options are more limited than some of the other brand they offer enough to get your basics covered If youve mostly worn converse stan smiths or air force s and want to venture into some premium options this is a good way to get your feet wet without breaking the bank Youre getting great leather while sacrificing some styling and construction but thats likely why the theyre able to come in at this price point 

 Uniform Standard  or  with shipping and promo code

Next up we have Uniform Standards Series  coming in at  british pounds which is roughly  as of me posting this video There are  off codes available to bring them down slightly I got these in their classic triple white in a size  after they recommended me to size up from what I wear in Common Projects They fit as I wanted them to

Uniform Standard is based out of East London with the shoes being made in Portugal with Italian leather Theyre a newer company started in  and I couldnt find too many reviews on them so I decided to give them a shot 

 Leather
    The leather was stiff coming out of the box but you can sense the quality The outer is made from full grain Italian calf leather thats sourced from environmentally friendly tanneries The inner leather feels slightly more supple and features a non slip suede rear thats much more textured than most Sock lints sometime get caught up in fairly easily 
 Soles
    The sole is made of partially recycled rubber and is fairly tall at an inch and a half compared to the rest On foot it feels near identical to the rest of the shoes so not much to say here but it feels more durable than Thursdays The leather lined foam insole provide provide cushioning on the heel and feature activated carbon coating to help with odors 
 Styling
    These are pretty minimal in their shape and feature some tasteful branding with the stitching detail on the rear and the debossed Uniform on the left foot and Standard on the right The toe box is wider than the rest but they dont look bulky by any means They were the most comfortable out of the box and Id recommend them the most for people with wider feet trying to find some minimal leather sneakers I especially like the outer heel which is short and slopes inward to follow the natural shape of your foot giving these a clean look from rear and side
 Conclusion
    There wasnt much to say about these shoes in general which is kinda telling on how to sum these up Theyre a solid reliable pair coming in at a decent price point with no frills attached to them Theyre about as boring as it gets which is a compliment as thats kinda the point with minimal leather sneakers 

 Oliver Cabell  but their base price fluctuates depending on the sale theyre running 

When you cross into the  mark youre going to pretty much get the same features and build throughout Oliver Cabell was out to directly compete with the CPs as well see with all the similarities These are the Oliver Cabell Low s in a Nude color way in a size  which ended up fitting like a EU  Their pricing annoys me as they run sales everyday and change the base price frequently depending on what percent they want to give off that particular day The final price is pretty much always  which is still up from the  that they used to be Nonetheless theyre the cheapest made in Italy with Italian leather and Italian soles showcased here 

 Leather
    The leather on these sneakers is amongst the best There have been reports its even sourced from the same Italian tanneries that CP uses The inner and upper is made from full grain Italian calfskin leather and its dyed in this pinkish nude color Its been surprisingly more versatile than I expected The leather is stiffer than most of the others making it slightly harder to break in but the wider cut helped with not making my feet hurt initially like some of the others did 
 Soles
    The soles are made by a brand called Margom which is industry best Theyre made in Italy and the best brands around the world use them The durability and rubber quality are very high delaying signs of heel drag and flat spots compared to alternatives The sole is shorter than the rest measuring in at less than an inch at its tallest point 
 Styling 
    The minimal styling is really showcased on this sneaker compared to the prior ones and compete directly with the common projects They are cut low and feature minimal paneling There is some foam padding around the ankle and in the tongue but not as much as the Thursday or the Uniform Standards The branding is minimal with a screen printed gold logo on the tongue and on the rear It lacks the foil shine the CPs branding has I like the angled touch on tongue and the overall paneling of the shoe The toe box has a subtle taper to it a slight nod to what CP is known for but no where near as aggressive 
 Build Quality
    The construction on these is where most of your money goes The sole is stitched glued and nailed to the upper A shank is present in the sole to prevent them for over flexing The footbed is made of fiberboard which is supposed to to easy for your feet to conform to but mine have been struggling for some reason causing them to still feel hard These are machine lasted unlike the hand lasted Common Projects and the Crown Northamptons well talk about in a bit The insert features the same leather as the inner and a subtle spongy feel In terms of construction and features these are identical to the Common Projects
    My pair had some inconsistencies with the stitching on the leather and on the midsole which is pretty disappointing at this price point  The soles also looked uneven with one sloping slightly downward shown at the  mark in the video Other reviews on Reddit have also pointed out some quality control issues with Oliver Cabell so be sure to inspect your pair well upon receiving them
 Conclusion
    This is going to be your entry level Italian minimal sneaker Although its over  its still a competitive price for everything youre getting 

 KOIO  but currently  

KOIOs Capris are up next coming in currently at  but normally at  They suggested sizing down unless unless I had a wide foot so I went with the s in this Limestone colorway Its a stunning creambeige that Ive really been loving A great departure from the normal white and grey I normally wear These are also fully made in Italy from the assembly to the leather and soles themselves 

 Leather
    KOIO uses a full grain cow leather for the inner and the outer They feel very similar to the Common Projects leather They are not as stiff as the Oliver Cabells and feel more comfortable out of the box 
 Soles
    These feature the same Margom soles as the CPs and the OCs that we talked about  Apparently they recently switched to a proprietary sole that they claim is the same if not better than Margom Might want to confirm this with their team prior to ordering 
 Construction
    The construction is also very similar to the CPs and OCs with the filler foam heel nails the compressed cardboard steel shank fiberboard insole all being the same 
    The insert differs being made by Ortholite and provides a nice bounce to your walk giving these a nice bounce Theyre as comfy as leather sneakers can get 
    The counter is also different being made of a reinforced fabric that wont break or snap when bent The sidewall is stitched to the leather without glue being used allowing you to resole these if need be The raw leather edges are painted to give them a cleaner look and prevent staining from denim 
 Styling
    They do feature more paneling then the common projects which one could argue are less minimal but I find them tastefully done with the stepped layers The toes have an aggressive taper and are narrower than the OCs but wider than the CPs Its a great shape and the silhoette is near identical to the CPs The tongue has no padding at all which allows the natural leather to shine through which I really like The ankle and heel has more padding than the CPs causing them to look ever so lightly bulkier but its honestly marginal
 Conclusion
    While the OCs were identical in construction and build to the CPs these are identical in construction build and styling Its genuinely hard to tell the difference unless you have a trained eye and they come in significantly cheaper There is more branding with the KOIOs letter debossed into the heels leather the outsole and the tongue but it being tone on tone makes it subtle
    Overall I think this is a great pickup especially if you can catch them on sale at  Youre getting stellar construction great looks Italian made a load of colors all for under 

 Crown Northhampton  

Down to our last two starting with the Crown Northampton Harlestone Hand Stitch Derby in Black Horween Buffalo Leather These are  made in as the name suggests Northampton England with many methods that are typically seen on hand welted dress shoes These are at a completely different league compared to the rest of the ones here and might be one of the nicest pair of leather sneakers on the market in terms of quality and construction Noting that theyre still cheaper than CPs coming in at  The brand has been around for over a hundred years and theyre still making shoes exactly as they used to which is the best possible compliment I can give in a fast fashion day and age 

 Leather
    The buffalo Horween leather on these is phenomenal Its tanned in the US with a combination of vegetable and chrome tanning The tanning process reduces the hide roughly  causing the fibers to be pulled tighter making the leather tougher and more durable than others while still being buttery smooth They leave a natural finish on the leather causing each pair to look slightly different from another Theres a natural pebbling and rippling across these that cant be compared to regular cow leather These are available in plenty of leather finishes and colors for you to choose from Leathers like these are typically reserved for high end dress shoes retailing in the thousands so its nice seeing them make their way into a pair of sneakers 
 Soles
    Anchoring it down are soles hand made in France by Lactae Hevea Theyre made from a latex rubber that goes through a  day curing process that gives them unrivaled comfort with a cushiony feel while remaining durable These feel like UltraBoosts compared to the rest of the lineup lol Since these are made to order you can actually choose your sole color I opted for this off white one but they also have a gum and black colored one I think a pure white would be a nice option to add as theyd go really well with the colors Crown Northampton offers The lack of glue used to secure these allows them to be fully resoled in the future if need be 
 Construction
    The construction is where this thing really shines There is no padding anywhere on the sneaker really allowing the leather to be the sole star The footbed is corkfilled by hand which will compress and allow your feet to mould to the bed giving these a semi Birkenstock type feel after the mold
    The heel counter is made from oak bark leather which is the best it gets and they use a full vegetable tanned leather for the inner lining Brands normally skimp here bc you dont need the best leather on the inside but Im glad CNH took the extra step
 Styling
    As the model suggests the only sign of branding are three pairs of hand stitches on each shoe Two in the front and one in the rear The laces feel like they were taken off a pair of their nicest dress shoes These are as minimal as they get with no unnecessary padding or logos The dust bags were also super high quality and impressive enough to worth noting They feature a straight shilouette with a slight taper once you hit the toe box 
 Conclusion
    Theyre handmade so they take some time to come in but boy are they worth waiting for These are by far the best and highest quality sneakers here and will only look better as more and more miles are put on them Even though theyre priced at  stacking them against the rest of these doesnt seem fair They seem to be in a category of their own with insanely high attention to detail and oozing quality throughout
     If you want the best crafted shoes thatll last decades so long as you resole them  look no further than these Its reassuring to know there are still brands out there who dont want clout or hype and just want to produce the best possible item they can at a reasonable price point for what youre getting If CP made a shoe of this caliber I have no doubt it would be priced in the four figures 

 Common Projects  

We all know Common Projects and what they offer by now so Ill keep it brief as its pretty much exactly like the KOIO and the OCs The first vid on the channel was dedicated to them in its entirety  I cringe watching it but the info is still relevant lmao 

 General Thoughts
    The feature a compressed leather counter unlike CNHs full oak bark leather The margom sole is secured with stitches on the side so theyll be able to be resoled if need be The heel is hand lasted and features brass nails to give it extra durability
    The common projects pionieered this entire minimal leather sneaker thing and have remained a cult favorite Ive been a fan for the longest time but as I said in my first video on this channel At  they arent worth it especially with Crown Northampton providing the level of sneaker they do at  cheaper and KOIO matching common projects at sub  However there is an element of design that needs to be taken into consideration

 VerdictTLDR

So what am I going to be replacing my beat up Common Projects with The thing I look for most in minimal leather sneakers are that narrow silhouette tapered toe and minimal padding In my opinion its this combination that helps these shoes go so well with everything you throw at them As similar as the KOIOs are I still think the Common Projects look marginally better which is why Ill be opting for fresh pair of those that I picked up on sale 

Different scenarios warrant different picks for me If I need a pair of minimal leather sneakers asap and I dont have time to wait for Common Projects to go on sale Im going KOIO 

If I want the best of the best with attention to detail second to none Im going Crown Northampton 

If Im new to the minimal sneaker game coming from Air Forces Stan Smiths or ConverseVans and want to get my feet wet Id start with the Uniform Standards as theyre quite a big jump up in quality than the Thursdays The Oliver Cabells are a nice entry to the Italian sneakers and may be better for people with wider feet

In terms of aesthetic

  Im sticking with the Common Projects followed closely by KOIO then Crown Northampton Oliver Cabell Uniform Standard then Thursdays 

In terms of quality 

 Im going Crown Northamptons and tie the KOIO Common Projects and Uniform Standard since theyre all built nearly the same way Ill follow this by Oliver Cabell due to the QC issues but if you find a perfect pair then theyre up there with the rest of the Italian made ones Ill finish with Thursday 

In terms of value 

 Uniform Standard takes the prize when it comes to value since it gives you similar constructions to the Italian shoes while coming in at significantly lower cost

I woke up early the next morning Like really early I looked over at Roses alarm clock It was  AM

Carefully I got up and checked on Rose She was sound asleep At the very least I could feel at ease knowing she was definitely having a good dream

I snuck out into the living room Thats when I heard Mom and Martin talking

Yeah I know it isnt the most polite thing in the world I get it But when its your Mom and the man she likes who wouldnt eavesdrop

Without making a sound I crept to the edge of the hallway wall and listened in on their conversation

You should tell her the truth Martin said She deserves to know

I know that but I also know if I tell her shell be hurt

Shes a tough kid I can tell

Who were they talking about Me or Rose

But if she finds out the truth before you tell her that will upset her more Martin added

I know how to raise my child

There was silence after that

I peeked around the corner to see Martin and Mom standing across from one another near the tree Mom had her arms crossed Martin stood there with a slight frown Im sorry Victoria I know you do I wasnt trying to suggest anything else He got closer wrapping his arms around my mom gently 

Mom wrapped her arms around him in return Its okay I know youre only concerned about Lupa

So it was me they were talking about

Then they kissed Im not sure why but seeing that made me feel awful It made me feel angry It was like watching Mom betray our family I could almost imagine Dad sitting up on Olympus watching this happen

I stepped out causing Martin to notice me Lupa He asked breaking from the kiss

Lupa Mom said turning to face me

There were so many things I wanted to say To yell about But everything just hurt so much I turned away and ran

Wait My mom yelled after me

I slammed into Martins door and swung it open then I turned into the hallway and booked it as fast as I could from the apartment building 

After a while I ended up in Central Park on a small bridge It felt so much like back in camp when Chanel bullied me Like the entire world was ending

I sat and I cried Again I failed I wasnt able to keep the promise I made

There was no chance of our family ever being complete Dad wasnt coming home And Mom shes moved on too But Im still here

Things stayed like that for half an hour Then I heard a womans voice calling from nearby Help She yelled Please

What was going on I stood and looked to see where the yelling was coming from It seemed to come from a wooded area

I took Diligence from my pocket and slid the bolt manifesting the celestial bronze blade in my grasp I didnt know what was going on but if someone was in trouble I had to at least try to help them

As silently as I could I snuck through the woods looking for whoever was yelling for help An owl hooted nearby causing me to jump I swung toward the sound of it and saw a branch sway Guess it flew away

There didnt seem to be any sign of anyone having been here Then I heard someone whisper psst

I swung toward the sound only for another whisper to come from elsewhere Psst over here a girls voice called

Someone was messing with me Hello I whispered back shuffling toward where I thought the voice came from

Something seemed seriously off about whatever was going on This was a stupid idea I was almost going to turn around and walk away when the snare got me I shot up into the air and hit my head on the ground as I went up My sword clattered from my hands Everything was hazy far away Below me I saw two shapes exit from the shadows Both of them were laughing Look brother we caught another

I groaned at them in protest as I dangled by my foot

Shut up dummy youre gonna make a really good stew the other said He sniffed the air You smell like an Olympians brat too he bellowed in laughter They always taste better

This was really it This was the end This was how I was going to die chopped up and made into some monsters stew I ruined Christmas and now I was going to break everyones hearts by dying too

I watched the two shapes from above as they talked

Something caught the moonlight A spear skewered one monster through the chest causing it to collapse and dissolve into dust

The remaining monster looked toward where the spear had come from and bellowed in anger Coward Come out

Someone exited from the shadows a spear in one hand a shield in the other They advanced toward the monster who circled around Soon they were like two wolves in a clearing just looking for the chance to pounce on one another

You killed my brother the monster grumbled Im gonna kill you too godling

Oh relax hell be back I mean unless hes too stupid to find the way out of Tartarus the man chuckled taunting the monster His voice I know that voice But from where

The monster took the bait and rushed him With one good thrust from his spear it was over The monster dissolved into dust

Whoever it was they looked up at me then looked around the area A few seconds later they lowered me to the ground 

Their face seemed familiar but I just couldnt put it to a name Youre okay here They took something from their pocket and brought it up to my mouth I tried to fight back of course but it was no use Something warm slid down my throat It tasted like smores Immediately the pain lessened Nectar

I coughed a few times as they picked me up and held me in their arms Lets go home

Despite my best efforts I fell asleep in their arms

A while later I woke up Not sure how much time passed it was still dark I looked up at their face everything was still hazy Dad I whispered

They looked down at me and their face slowly came into focus Martin

Afraid not he said softly You gave your mom quite the scare Lucky I found you before you became cyclops stew

I thought for a while about what to say Youre a demigod I whispered

Yep Just like you

Whos your parent

Its not obvious He asked chuckling

I shook my head

Athenas my mother My eyes are normally gray but I use contacts to set myself apart just a little Youre wearing contacts too right

No

A surprised look swept over his face Really Wow you have really bright green eyes

Im sorry I said

He sighed Its okay I knew something like this might happen Its why I told your mom that she needed to be honest with you

Thinking about what I saw back in the apartment made me sad I closed my eyes and tried not to cry again  

MUSIC  

Its okay to cry Lupa Martin whispered

This wasnt how things were supposed to be

Martin kept quiet

I just wanted it to be me and Mom Or for Dad to come and be with us But now I know hes never gonna come and see us Its not fair I just want to have a family like everyone else

Saying those words broke the dam I hated it I didnt want to cry or be sad anymore

And I ruined everyones Christmas I made my mom worried put you in danger And I just keep making the same mistakes When am I going to learn When am I going to be better than this

If you ask me I think youre ready now

What

The first part of bettering ourselves is acknowledging our mistakes and working to try to not make them again You cant undo the past but the future is yours to write

Are you gonna tell my mom

He shook his head No Call me a hypocrite but I think its better if she doesnt know you were almost monster chow Besides you learned a lesson and the nectar will heal your injuries Everything will be okay

Does she know youre a demigod

Martin frowned and sighed again No she doesnt But seeing as how youre a demigod too I think its time I told her the truth

How come you didnt tell her before

I didnt want to freak her out Or make her think that Im crazy Shes just a regular person

That made sense

So I take it then that when she said you were with your dad that really means that you were at camp

I nodded Yeah youve been there too

Yeah I stayed at camp until I was  Then I went to college

Something else crossed my mind Howd you find me by the way

Oh right

Martin whistled loudly and five owls flew from the nearby trees and landed at his feet I can summon owls and have them scout for me Its somewhat useful

He took a step forward and the owls flew away in different directions 

What about you Whos your Dad Martin asked

Hermes I whispered

Ah Now that you mention it I can kind of see the resemblance You definitely took after your dad a lot

Youve seen my dad

Well no Ive never met him But I have seen depictions of him

There was silence for a few minutes before Martin spoke again Im sorry about your dad Lupa I know what its like to want your parent to be there for you When I was younger I felt the same way

Do   do you really care about me I asked

Martin stopped abruptly and looked down at me Of course Would I have come out here to find you if I didnt

He made a good point

Im sorry

Its okay Its understandable that you would ask that question I get it Id probably wonder the same thing to be honest he said moving again

Rose Shes a demigod too

Are you going to tell her

When the time is right Yes I think when she turns  Its usually around that time that the monsters notice us

Shes already really powerful Her powers theyre amazing

Ah she paid a visit to your dreams

I nodded Yeah She tried to help me

Shes kind Sometimes I have nightmares too

You do

Martin nodded at my question Yes he whispered Ive seen a lot of things in my life so far This life our lives they arent easy And more often than not theyre tragic Im just trying to be as happy as possible while Im here

How do you deal with it

With the nightmares

I nodded

I went to therapy I know a therapist actually shes a demigod too In fact shes actually a sister of yours

She is

Yeah Is this apartment  I was asked to deliver a letter here by someone

Um yeah  

The man reached into his pocket and took out an envelope He handed it to Martin and grinned Happy holidays

Uh thanks You too

Martin closed the door and walked back over to us Weird

Whos it from

Dunno There are no markings on it

He broke the seal and opened the letter After a few seconds he handed it to me Its for you

Me I said confused

I took the letter and looked it over There were two words written on the inside along with a symbol a caduceus wrapped with a heart

My Child  

MUSIC  

Mom walked beside me and looked at it She seemed confused and to be honest I was at first too Then the more I thought about it the more I understood It was his answer to my question I asked myself what I was to Zeus and Apollo and this was his answer I was his child He was listening to me Watching over me He heard my prayer last night and this was him answering it

I stared at the letter for a long time His voice I could almost imagine him saying those words to me It made my heart ache

Nothing could ever make up for him not being here But I know he cant be Its the same for all demigods I looked at Martin Rose and Mom and I smiled Mom wrapped her arm around me and pulled me close

There werent any words Just warmth And as I looked at Martins apartment it seemed like home No it didnt just seem like it It felt like it too Its hard to describe You know that feeling when youve been away from home for a really long time and you finally get back Thats the feeling

What do you guys say we open the rest of the presents Martin asked stepping close to us

Yeah Rose said laughing

Things didnt turn out the way I thought they would but they did turn out well

Eventually all the presents were open I had several books to read and a few new pieces of clothing But the real gift as cheesy as it sounds and believe me this ones going to sound like a cheese lasagna was the people around me Mom Martin Rose Im still not sure how to feel about everything but Im glad

Martin and Rose came with us to the car later that day The four of us stood there saying our goodbyes You can come back and see us any time you want Lupa There will always be a place for you here Think about what I asked as well Send me an IM if you decide you want to talk to her okay

Okay I nodded

Rose stepped up Goodbye hug

I smiled Yeah

And the two of us hugged Mom joined us next then Martin I felt so happy So warm It almost made me want to cry This was it This was what I had been searching for the whole time I love you guys I whispered my voice shaky My Father My Dad II

This is the second part of Olyas story Like the first part the bold text will include a summary as well as commentary from timetotime The plain text is quotations from the article verbatim



She begins talking about her state of mind after she attempted suicide in Geneva She says she tried to talk to Zverev about it but he did not want to talk about it and offered her no emotional support

Sharypova said she attended a preevent Laver Cup banquet and then the Laver Cup matches including Zverevs win over Milos Raonic that clinched a comefrombehind win for Team Europe

I was happy for him I was so proud of him Sharypova said of Zverevs victory I loved himof course I was proud But she said she also asked for him to acknowledge the hurt hed caused as she tried to improve her emotional wellbeing Its not normal that Im a person who doesnt want to live and its because of our relationship

Sharypova said that to her disappointment Zverev did not show contrition Traveling on tour with him from hotel to hotel apart from friends and family also made it hard for her to get steady support

They went to China next and had another fight at once but he was more eventempered so she felt like she could live with him

After the Laver Cup Sharypova accompanied Zverev to China where he played in the China Open in Beijing and the Rolex Shanghai Masters In Beijing she said the couple got into another argument but she said she found Zverev more eventempered than hed been in their previous disagreements

He was really calmed down and he was more controlling himself she said For me it was like OK now we can live together Now I feel more protected Safer

But the stress had caused her skin to break out Mrs V had joined her in China and Zverev said that she would be the first person invited to their wedding

The stress of recent weeks however had caused Sharypovas skin to break out adding to her distress and drawing insults on social media Sharypova showed me an Instagram account with only one post a closeup of her facial acne

In Shanghai Sharypova was looking forward to being joined by Mrs V the stepmother of her friend Vasil Surduk Mrs V had given Sharypova a place to stay when she had fled Zverev in New York and then persuaded Sharypova to go back to him

Sascha had said that when we have a wedding the first invitation will be for her Sharypova said

Their next fight happened because Mrs V gifted them a bag of fruit that Olya unpacked in their hotel After she was finished unpacking it her and Mrs V went to a nearby salon to treat her skin When Zverev came back to the hotel he was upset about the fruit and started texting her nonstop It is unclear why he was upset about this but he became even angrier when she was not there waiting for him in the hotel He wanted her to come back to him right away

her house in Phuket Thailand bringing the couple a large bag of fruit as a gift Sharypova said she unpacked the fruit in the couples room at the Kunlun Jing An the official tournament hotel She then went with Mrs V to the tournament where they watched Zverev win his roundof match over Jeremy Chardy After the match Sharypova said Zverev was scheduled for training and recovery sessions so she went with Mrs V to a nearby salon where the pair planned to get their nails done and have facial treatments that Sharypova hoped would help her skin

Sharypova said that while at the salon she received a flurry of messages from Zverev
He sent me pictures with the fruit and said Why is this here  Sharypova said He starts to fight with me about the fruits which I put on his massage table because I was in a hurry

Sharypova said that only three weeks after the incident in Geneva she couldnt summon the energy for another fight with Zverev

He started saying Why did I come home and youre not here I need to clean this Youre not here why are you at the salon why am I waiting for you You dont love me And I was like What are you talking about Im always waiting for you in the room Im not fighting with you when youre somewhere else Can I have a little space for a few hours to take care of my face 

When Olya finally returned to the hotel Zverev left the hotel immediately claiming that she would have to wait for him since she made him wait for her She understood that when he came back it would be another fight even though she tried to talk it out with him

When she returned to the hotel room Sharypova said Zverev left immediately

He said I was waiting for you Now you should wait for me  she recalled I understood that when he will come back it will be another fight another story and I dont want it I asked for help and I asked for his understanding but I got nothing

Dreading another fight she tried to commit suicide again She injected herself with the insulin She didnt have the energy for it anymore

I was in the room alone I was thinking about all this stuff I wanted to just pick up my stuff and go but I dont know where I dont know what Im supposed to do At this time because of my nervous system I didnt think a lot I just did it again

Sharypova said that for the second time in a month she injected herself with insulin while Zverev was not in the room to stop her

I just dont want to fight she said recounting her feelings at the time I just dont have energy for it I was just lying in bed and thats all

This time Zverev saved her from suicide He fed her a packet of sugar and as soon as she started to recover he started yelling at her She offered to break up with him and fly home to Moscow but he declined

When Zverev returned to the room Sharypova said she was barely responsive
He understood that something had happened Sharypova said I was too calm When he checked my sugar it was  milligrams per decilitera lifethreateningly low level

Sharypova said that Zverev fed her a package of sugar she was too weak to resist After she began to recover she said Zverev berated her again

He asked me Why did you do this to me You understand what you did to me right now He starts yelling at me and saying that if you will die in my room it will be big problems for me Its really a big responsibility for me You said that you dont want to live because of mewhy did you say this 

Sharypova said that she offered to break up with Zverev and fly home to Moscow Zverev declined Sharypova said but he said that she had made it difficult for him to focus on playing his next match

 I live with this  Sharypova says she told him  I understand its hard for you but you can realize how its worse for me I was writing to people that I didnt want to live I was crying I was always crying Every day I was crying

The next morning another fight happened He claimed he was the real victim and told her to go fuck herself

Sharypova said she still felt lost when she woke up the next morning Oct  I didnt have feelings emotions words she told me He started to blame me again and to say that hes really the victim of the situation

Zverev suggested that Sharypova shouldnt attend his match against Andrey Rublev later that day and she agreed

I was already at the very bottom she said And he said If its like that you should pack your stuff and go fuck yourself I said OK I will fly to Moscow You will come back and I will be somewhere else 

She went to take a shower He followed her into the bathroom and started berating her outside of it He wanted her to pack her belongings and leave right away She told him he would have to wait because she was naked He attacked her then grabbing her by the throat and pushing her up against the hard tile of the bathroom wall

Sharypova said she went to take a shower during which Zverev continued berating her from outside the bathroom door

When I got out of the shower I was starting to take a towel and he came and said Pack your stuff right now and leave  Sharypova recalled Im just like OK can you wait a few minutes please Im naked here 

From there Sharypova said Zverev attacked her more violently than he ever had before She said that he grabbed her by the throat and pushed her up against the hard tile wall of the bathroom

She says he started punching her and she started fighting back This time she would not just take it

He started to punch me and this time I understand that I cant be dough for punching she said

Sharypova said she began swinging her arms wildly to fend off Zverev as best she could

I was just trying to protect myself she said Im already naked Im a woman I dont have much power And after my shower I dont have time to get my clothes I dont feel safe for one second

Amidst the physical assault he started verbally assaulting her as well telling her that he hopes she dies but not in his room He told her to take insulin and go die in the streets Olya starts crying telling him that she will

Sharypova said that Zverev was also insulting her amid the physical blows

He started to say to me these things I hope you will die you should have died yesterday but not in my room If you want to die you can take insulin and go die in the street because I dont want problems I dont want to deal with you anymore  she remembered Im crying I say OK if you want me to die give me insulin I go to the street and thats all I cant hear this anymore I cant handle anymore What do you want from me You want to punch me You already did 

He eventually stopped and called someone on his phone while she locked herself in the bathroom It turned out to be his father who came to their room and told her to pack her belongings and leave by evening Zverevs father threatened her telling her that they would sue her if she didnt leave and how he has evidence of her punching his son He called her trash

Sharypova said that Zverev eventually called someone on his phone and left the room After she locked herself in the bathroom she said she heard another voice through the door Zverevs father Alexander Zverev Sr

 You have until evening to pack your stuff  Sharypova recalled Zverev Sr telling her He said If you dont leave I will sue you because I have photos of how you punched my son 

I was naked sitting on the floor of the showerall my body burns she said When he left I was so emotionally down I just started laughing I was crying and I was laughing His father just was like Youre trash We dont need you 

Twelve hours later Zverev played another match and there were scratch marks on the side of his neck Olya says those marks came from her defending herself Footage from his previous match confirms that those scratches were not there the day before during his match against Jeremy Chardy

When Zverev took the court for his roundof match roughly  hours later there were scratch marks on the left side of his neck Those marks which Sharypova told me resulted from their fight are clearly visible in wire photos as well as in match and interview footage Footage from his previous match against Jeremy Chardy confirms the scratches werent present the day before

Footage from that Oct  match against Chardy also shows Sharypova sitting in the courtside players box Shes not present in that box for any of Zverevs subsequent matches in Shanghai starting with the Rublev match on the evening of Oct 

Two days later Olya sent pictures of her bruised face and arms to her friend Olya had since gotten a new phone but the friend still had the pictures and shared them though they asked not be named In the messages Olya says This is Sascha and explains how it had gotten worse

Sharypova said that two days after Zverev attacked her in the bathroom she used WhatsApp to send images of her stillbruised face and arms to a close friend shed confided in before

Though Sharypova has gotten a new phone since then and did not archive her messages her friend still has the record of their conversation

I spoke to Sharypovas friend who asked not to be named in this article last week She told me Sharypova had spoken to her frequently during her relationship with Zverev keeping her apprised of what Sharypova described as a pattern of escalating abuse

Usually were open about anything and everything but after New York she was keeping to herself more than usual and I knew something was going on the friend told me I knew after New York it was going to be even worse And I told her Why would you after all this happened in New York give him another chance If he did this once hes going to do the same thing Then a week after wed spoken the last time she sent me these pictures

Whats this the friend texted in response to the images of Sharypovas bruises

This is Sascha Sharypova responded
What the hell her friend said Him again

The same happened in Geneva 

Sharypova answered In Geneva he started to punch in the face

Olya reaches out to Mrs V and asks for help because she has no money and nowhere to stay Mrs V says Olya came to her She saw her bruises and kept her safe

Mrs V told me she traveled to Shanghai in  with her youngest son a sports fan to see the happy reconciliation of Zverev and Sharypovathe couple she had worked to reunite in New York a month earlier She sat courtside next to Sharypova in Zverevs players box during his win against Jeremy Chardy on Oct 

The next day in the afternoon we were supposed to get in touch Mrs V told me But by  oclock nobody had gotten in touch nothing All of the sudden Olyaa diminutive of Olgacalls my number and says that shes in a bad situation she doesnt know what to do shes screwed she has no money no place to stay I said Come up 

Mrs V said that at this point she wasnt sure what had happened between Zverev and Sharypova She said that Zverev was continuing to text her wanting her to convince Sharypova to reunite with him once more

She was all bluegreen crying and everything Mrs V told me If I saw something maybe some scratches I didnt take pictures or make a big deal out of it I never thought it was going to come to this point and since the guy was still talking and wanting her back and I wasnt exactly sure what happened I didnt know what to do All I could do was keep her safe which I did

Olya told Mrs V that she tried to commit suicide Mrs V texted Zverev and he confirmed Mrs V said she was nasty with Olya because she had no right to try and take her own life

Mrs V said Sharypova told her about how she had injected herself with insulin for a second time after their argument Mrs V said that it made her furious

I was nasty with her Mrs V said I told her she has no right to play with her own life like that because she has parents who love her shes only something years old
Mrs V showed me a text exchange she had with Zverev from Oct   In those texts written in Russian Zverev acknowledged Sharypovas two incidents of insulin selfinjection

I spoke harshly to her about the insulin Mrs V wrote

Its not the first time Zverev replied

Mrs V did not take Olya back home to Moscow Instead she had Olya stay with her for two months She kicked her husband out of their shared bedroom and stayed by Olyas side scared that she would try to commit suicide again She would not leave the room She felt responsible for the abuse because she had encouraged Olya to reconcile with him

Fearing that she might harm herself a third time Mrs V refused to allow Sharypova to travel back to Moscow as the Zverevs had wanted

Instead Mrs V booked a larger room at the Kunlun Jing An and had Sharypova stay there with her while her son continued to attend the tennis tournament

I stayed with Olya I didnt even leave the room basically Mrs V said

I have to stick to my initial thing of them being just untrue and continue to deny them Zverev said It makes me sad the impact that such false accusations can haveon the sport on the outside world on myself as well I truly apologize that the focus has shifted away from the sport We all love playing tennis Thats what were here to do
